msg: Fix copy cross detection, and fix an off-by-one problem related to
those checks.  This is all about issue #1003 -
(revisions_changed_callback): Compare paths, too, when looking for
copy boundary crossing.  Also, don't clear the successor_id field
at the end of processing (just set the 'done' flag).
'successor_id' baton members, and detect copy crossings here, too.
